{"tid":986306,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)異形1 3 4","createTime":"2019-01-18T10:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T17:28:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7cc7a530c2134d3ed381c29a91af26f0988e7f8a","tid":986306,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=85adf695\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=1392bb0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=7ea9a091\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c3/Alien_movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc3%2FAlien_movie_poster.jpg&h=58e3e478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一架載有7名船員、名叫Nostromo的商業星際運載船，正將2千萬噸礦物由Thedus行星運送回地球。在電影開始時，被船員稱為母親的太空船電腦MU-TH-R 182收到一個來自鄰近星球、無法解析的訊號。「母親」將正在冬眠狀態的船員們喚醒，使他們能夠去偵察訊號的來源。醒來的船員們把礦物及提煉設施留在行星軌道，用Nostromo的拖曳用太空船登陸該星球，但機體被粗糙的星球表面造成了部份損壞........<br />\n<br />\n2.在電影的一開始，第一集中Nostromo的唯一一個人類生還者&mdash;&mdash;陸軍少尉艾倫&middot;雷普利（Ellen Ripley，雪歌妮&middot;薇佛），在太空獲救，並於57年的超睡眠後甦醒過來。醒來後，由於Ripley爆破了Nostromo，為了釐清責任，因此她的僱主Weyland-Yutani公司舉行了聽證會。由於沒有確切的物理證據証明在Nostromo摧毀時有不明生物存在，因此她的證詞被所有人懷疑而不被採信，而最後也因為她的「可疑的決定」，公司撤銷了Ripley的太空飛行執照......<br />\n<br />\n3.在上一部《異形3》中的故事200年後，死去的Ripley被軍方和公司的科學家復製出來，並成功地從其腹中取出了一具異形。而Ripley的基因里也帶上了異形的基因，使得她變得更加強壯。但是異形超強的繁殖能力和生長速度以及超乎想像的智慧，使得局勢很快失去控制。異形逃出了豢養它們的牢籠，在太空船上大開殺戒。為了不讓這些嗜血成性的生物來到地球上，Ripley必須想方設法殺死自己的「骨肉」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n4.又殺我隻狗1-2掛<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=607cbb99\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=d645c124\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccfc6318e610da6a4aa4583ab6999e5523e2b44","tid":986306,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:33:20.000Z","msg":"1 2 4先岩注意"},{"pid":"339b219815e26a97a7e5997eeb0bb3050e5577b7","tid":986306,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no